sentences: Hedvig Mollestad Thomassen (born 4 February 1982) is a Norwegian guitarist, vocalist and composer.
Thomassen was awarded "The young jazz talent of the year" at Moldejazz in 2009, and played a gig within Jarle Bernhoft Band at the 2011 Kongsberg Jazzfestival.
